channel.title: Client Compiler
channel.description:
Hello everyone I downloaded a source + client to code for my new server, and i had a problem that i thought i can fix but i couldnt. The problem is that the client's compiler has 100 errors and all of them r ( cannot find symbol ). My friend have also downloaded the client and source but he didnt have errors at all. I have read a post saying inorder to fix that i will have to download the client all over again, and thats what i did, but i still got the same problem. If any1 can help me by telling me how to fix it or whats causing it I will be more than thankful for him.
Thanks.
